– courtesy of fast-loading SVGs – the theme pays special attention to styling post formats for visual variety. A perfect fit for sharing projects, recipes, and stories, Scratchpad is now available for download on WordPress.org.</p>\n<p><a href="https://scratchpaddemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6704" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/14/scratchpad/scratchpad-ss/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/scratchpad-ss.png?w=840" data-orig-size="720,540" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="scratchpad-ss" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/scratchpad-ss.png?w=840?w=300" data-large-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/scratchpad-ss.png?w=840?w=720" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6704" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/scratchpad-ss.png?w=840" alt="scratchpad-ss" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/scratchpad-ss.png 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/scratchpad-ss.png?w=150 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/scratchpad-ss.png?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px"   /></a></p><img alt="" border="0" src="https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6703&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:29:"http://search.yahoo.co